data.description: Welcome to this beautiful mid-century modern gem! This 4-bedroom residence boasts the potential for a 5th bedroom, making it a versatile and spacious home for your family. With 1 full bathroom and 2 half baths. One of the standout features of this home is the large loft space, perfect for use as an office, playroom, or even an additional bedroom, providing flexibility to accommodate your family's needs. When you're ready to unwind or entertain, step outside onto the inviting deck, overlooking the expansive backyard. The wooded surroundings offer a tranquil, country-like atmosphere, providing a sense of serenity and privacy. You'll feel like you're escaping to your own oasis, all while being conveniently located close to amenities and everything you need. This property truly offers the best of both worlds - a peaceful and secluded retreat with a spacious yard for family gatherings and outdoor enjoyment, all within a short distance from the conveniences of city life.
